  m_Name: u8_Brain
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  entityName: 
  entitySprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fa5dfd096c6e61742a7b552d75de9656, type: 3}
  introduction:
  - "Noted. Noted. Pending analysis\u2026 noted."
  actionSpeakFeedback:
  - Waste not my time, creature! There is much to acquire just beyond those doors.
  - I already know everything there is to know about the outside. Now let me through
    at once.
  - "...Impudent little doorman\u2026 noted."
  - Out there is destruction. And boredom. Everything interesting is long gone, and
    long known. But I see that in this place lies much to be studied. Merely waiting
    for a mind as immense as mine to graciously lend itself to it.
  - "I have long surpassed my ancestors\u2019 need for care and fellowship. I am
    the last of my kind, but it does not matter. They worked themselves to death
    providing for my existence, and they never even realised that I had no real use
    for them."
  - A being such as myself has no time for merriment or passion. Only fact is worth
    pursuing. Fact is the basis of existence. Everything else is trivial.
  - "Analysis update: remarkably insistent, obtuse, impudent little doorman\u2026"
  - An intelligence of my capacity is wasted out here. Not like simple creatures
    like you would understand.
  actionPokeFeedback:
  - "It\u2019s enormous. I question how it could\u2019ve even gotten here \u2013
    its body seems too fragile for the bloated protuberance it bears, swaying with
    every slow step. I can\u2019t recognise eyes or ears, but it seems to perceive
    me clearly. I hear its words right inside my head. It\u2019s too slow to move
    away when I touch it, so it screams another soundless complaint. Its surface
    is spongy and warm."
  sparedDialogue:
  - "Issue resolved, archived. Beginning new inquiry. Prepare to assess\u2026\r\\"
